OL,7,FOne notice in the shop states: "Due to
OL,8,Fa spate of shoplifting, we have taken
OL,9,Fthe decision to relocate the washing
OL,10,Fdetergent. We have placed them behind
OL,11,Fthe counter."JNow staff are asking
OL,12,Fregular shoppers to remain vigilant -
OL,13,Fand report any suspected criminals.
OL,14,FSteve said: "The police are on to it
OL,15,Fand we've put notices around the shop
OL,16,Fto say that certain items are now
OL,17,Fbeing kept behind the counter.
