OL,4,Cbehind counter in 'war against
OL,5,Cshoplifters'
OL,7,F"It's been ongoing for three or four
OL,8,Fyears, certain people were coming in
OL,9,Fand taking multiple items, such as
OL,10,Fchocolate, so they can sell it on
OL,11,Felsewhere.J"Some people take baby milk
OL,12,Fand washing detergent so we put them
OL,13,Fbehind the counter but then they take
OL,14,Fother things instead, such as meat,
OL,15,Fcoffee, chocolate, and whatever they
OL,16,Fcan sell quickly.
