OL,3,CShop hides baby milk and detergent
OL,4,Cbehind counter in 'war against
OL,5,Cshoplifters'
OL,7,F"It's usually the more expensive items
OL,8,Fand they don't just take one, they
OL,9,Ftake multiples of each item.J"We never
OL,10,Fused to get much shoplifting. It was
OL,11,Fjust before Covid started so it's
OL,12,Fnothing to do with people struggling
OL,13,Fbecause of the cost of living.
OL,15,F"I don't think the thieves are from
OL,16,Fthat far away, they'll park down the
OL,17,Froad or get dropped off so we don't
OL,18,Fcatch the vehicles they use on CCTV.
OL,19,F"The thing is we're a franchise, we're
OL,20,Fnot company owned, so whatever is
OL,21,Fstolen affects us directly.
